WEBVTT

00:01.440 --> 00:03.112
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:03.200 --> 00:05.111
So, are we staying yet?

00:05.200 --> 00:06.952
Are we exclusive yet?

00:08.600 --> 00:10.431
Game on, Brooke Davis.

00:11.480 --> 00:13.357
I would like to say something.

00:13.440 --> 00:15.556
Mayor Mullins, I object.

00:15.920 --> 00:19.071
Well, this is not a court of law, Dan.
Sit down.

00:25.840 --> 00:29.355
- I'm still your father.
- But you're not my father, are you?

00:29.440 --> 00:31.271
Divorce is fine, Deb.

00:32.759 --> 00:34.239
You seem surprised.

00:34.680 --> 00:35.829
Here.

00:36.520 --> 00:37.839
It's my cocaine vial.

00:38.360 --> 00:41.511
Thought you might like it,
considering you were buying drugs today.

00:42.440 --> 00:46.319
Ellie was buying marijuana.
But not for the reasons you think.

00:46.440 --> 00:49.637
She's sick. She has cancer, Peyton.

00:50.840 --> 00:52.592
<i>Always and forever.</i>

00:52.920 --> 00:55.798
That's what sucks, Haley.
I still do love you.

00:55.880 --> 00:57.757
I just can't trust you.

